communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Washington Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

I would like to see a copy of your agreement with Hinge Health, and any presentations shared with the city of Seattle about adoption, performance, and money saved. This includes

1: The contract between the city of Seattle and Hinge health. 
2: Any and all presentations related to launching Hinge health.
3: Ongoing  customer success presentations that show program utilization, including number of people starting and completing the program and ROI. These presentations may be called mid-year reviews, or annual reviews. An example from the city of Fort Worth can be viewed at this link: 
https://www.fortworthtexas.gov/files/assets/public/hr/documents/wellness/hinge-health-mid-year-review-2022-city-of-fort-worth.pdf 

thank you

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Joseph Hawilo
